adj_shp = NY_data %>% filter(Race == 'Latinx/Hispanic') %>% select("HIV diagnosis rate", "geometry") %>% mutate(sqrt_diagnosis_rate = sqrt(`HIV diagnosis rate`))

#boundaries need to be more than one point
